  "text": "For each given periodic switching signal σ, the above design problem can be solved efficiently via convex programs as before to find {Q m } n m=1 . However, it is still computationally expensive to find an optimal solution of a periodic switching signal and associated Youla parameters. Instead of an exhaust search, we adopt a heuristic search method from [CITATION_1] .",
